sets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去做個啲垃圾工囉，瘋狂send 求職信我唔信揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e7a1a784b1a1480ac979a85cff77f24565f72f","tid":292111,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n我有朋友都係咁<br />\n唔知中五定中六Quit左，無考DSE<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊到搵條友結左婚生埋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾有錢下"},{"pid":"84fbcc283396fd53a13608def07b42307e745090","tid":292111,"uid":121213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"你仲識上連登  仲識開post 仲識打中文<br />\n<br />\n智商應該夠搵份廢工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，做我條女得唔得？"},{"pid":"39bfd78ac5c462ea1c1fa63068e8a49921bd0c38","tid":292111,"uid":117093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畢業完冇做野<br />\n見過好多文職工都唔請<br />\n唔想再靠屋企錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你柒少陣啦，你英文普通話又唔得見文職？見條毛啦你。點解可以容許自己咁廢，兩年唔做嘢重要拎老豆老母錢去旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文職好多時個人重要好醒，特別係對客嘅好似銀行工。你連無嘢做嘅時候都重要揀擇你話俾我聽你有幾醒？你話唔想勞力連M記都唔做，你個人係真係值咁多咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做你啲你可以做咩？ 重話想結婚？你估啲仔真係個個9公傻的嗎？ 無學歷無內涵當你有個好啲嘅嘢都只係可以溝到MK仔或者9公。你再咁落去到你幾廿歲個時有無老公，又有個仔要去拎老綜我真係恭喜你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己係個社會值幾多都唔知，會唔會你連中文個醜字都以為係個醒字呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea752ecc192fc72b9aec46f8ab38d9ba611f80e","tid":292111,"uid":117093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 潛咗水?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b4a680433cf9